{
  "page": "Spearwife",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:T_Jedruszek_YoungSpearWife.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3e/T_Jedruszek_YoungSpearWife.jpg/300px-T_Jedruszek_YoungSpearWife.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3e/T_Jedruszek_YoungSpearWife.jpg/450px-T_Jedruszek_YoungSpearWife.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3e/T_Jedruszek_YoungSpearWife.jpg/600px-T_Jedruszek_YoungSpearWife.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:T_Jedruszek_YoungSpearWife.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A spearwife with a <a href=\"/index.php/Mammoth\" title=\"Mammoth\">mammoth</a>, by Tomasz Jedruszek © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>A <b>spearwife</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a> woman who is also <a href=\"/index.php/Woman_warrior\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Woman warrior\">a warrior</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Spearwife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Spearwife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Ygritte_by_steamey.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/97/Ygritte_by_steamey.jpg/250px-Ygritte_by_steamey.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"321\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/97/Ygritte_by_steamey.jpg/375px-Ygritte_by_steamey.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/97/Ygritte_by_steamey.jpg/500px-Ygritte_by_steamey.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Ygritte_by_steamey.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://steamey.deviantart.com\">Steamey©</a></div></div></div>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_ranging\" title=\"Great ranging\">great ranging</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> in the lands <a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Qhorin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Qhorin\">Qhorin</a>'s rangers encounter the spearwife <a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> and other raiders in the <a href=\"/index.php/Skirling_Pass\" title=\"Skirling Pass\">Skirling Pass</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Spearwife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Ragwyle\" title=\"Ragwyle\">Ragwyle</a> is part of <a href=\"/index.php/Rattleshirt\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rattleshirt\">Rattleshirt</a>'s band of raiders.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Jon sees long-haired spearwives in the host of <a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance Rayder</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_beneath_the_Wall\" title=\"Battle beneath the Wall\">battle beneath the Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Spearwife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Varamyr_Sixskins\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Varamyr Sixskins\">Varamyr Sixskins</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">skinchanger</a>, attempts to take over a spearwife, <a href=\"/index.php/Thistle\" title=\"Thistle\">Thistle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Harwood_Fell\" title=\"Harwood Fell\">Harwood Fell</a> counts dozens of spearwives among the free folk who have surrendered to <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> Jon, now <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</a>, houses nineteen women and girls, including a dozen spearwives, in <a href=\"/index.php/Hardin%27s_Tower\" title=\"Hardin&#39;s Tower\">Hardin's Tower</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> Jon sends spearwives to garrison <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Barrow\" title=\"Long Barrow\">Long Barrow</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a> has a vision of a grey girl on dying horse, whom Jon believes is his half sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> Jon is convinced to release Mance and send him with six spearwives on a mission to rescue the girl.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> Disguised as the bard Abel, Mance infiltrates <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> with <a href=\"/index.php/Frenya\" title=\"Frenya\">Frenya</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Holly\" title=\"Holly\">Holly</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Myrtle\" title=\"Myrtle\">Myrtle</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Rowan\" title=\"Rowan\">Rowan</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Squirrel_(free_folk)\" title=\"Squirrel (free folk)\">Squirrel</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Willow_Witch-eye\" title=\"Willow Witch-eye\">Willow Witch-eye</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Spearwife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>She wasn't wed and her weapon of choice was a short curved bow of horn and <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood\" title=\"Weirwood\">weirwood</a>, but \"spearwife\" fit her all the same.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>'s thoughts regarding <a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Spearwife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_68\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 68\">Chapter 68</a>, Jon VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_51\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 51\">Chapter 51</a>, Jon VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_7\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 7\">Chapter 7</a>, Jon I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_73\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 73\">Chapter 73</a>, Jon X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.